  <ParaLine 
   <TextRectID 25>
   <String `Motorola reserves the right to make changes without further notice to any products herein.  Motorola makes no warranty, representation or guarantee regarding '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `the suitability of its products for any particular purpose, nor does Motorola assume any liability arising out of the application or use of any product or circuit, and '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `specifically disclaims any and all liability, including without limitation consequential or incidental damages. \xd2 Typical\xd3  parameters can and do vary in different '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `applications.  All operating parameters, including \xd2 Typicals\xd3  must be validated for each customer application by customer\xd5 s technical experts.  Motorola does not '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `convey any license under its patent rights nor the rights of others.  Motorola products are not designed, intended, or authorized for use as components in '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `systems intended for surgical implant into the body, or other applications intended to support or sustain life, or for any other application in which the failure of the '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `Motorola product could create a situation where personal injury or death may occur.  Should Buyer purchase or use Motorola products for any such unintended '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `or unauthorized application, Buyer shall indemnify and hold Motorola and its officers, employees, subsidiaries, affiliates, and distributors harmless against all '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `claims, costs, damages, and expenses, and reasonable attorney fees arising out of, directly or indirectly, any claim of personal injury or death associated with '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `such unintended or unauthorized use, even if such claim alleges that Motorola was negligent regarding the design or manufacture of the  part.  Motorola and '>
   <AFrame 1>
   <String ` '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `are registered trademarks of Motorola Inc.  Motorola, Inc. is an Equal Opportunity/Affirmative Action Employer.'>
  >
 > # end of Para
