 <Para 
  <Unique 68>
  <PgfTag `Body'>
  <ParaLine 
   <String `The 46226 is a 4,096,000 bit static random access memory organized as 131,072 '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `words of 8, 16, 24 or 32 bits. The module is constructed using four 6226 static RAM '>
  >
  <ParaLine 
   <String `die mounted in a multilayer co-fired hermetic ceramic sealed package.'>
  >
 > # end of Para
